ational Law Clinic, and the Human Rights Center, University of California, Berkeley Special Report. Laurel Fletcher, Phuong Pham, Eric Stover, and Patrick Vinck. June 2006 *{{cite book | last = Quigley | first = William | coauthors = Sharda Sekaran | editors = Soohoo, Cynthia; Albisa, Catherine; Davis, Martha F. | title = Bringing Human Rights Home: Portraits of the Movement | volume = III | chapter = A Call for the Right to Return in the Gulf Coast | pages = 291–304 | publisher = Praeger Publishers | year = 2007 | isbn = 0-275-98824-4}} *{{cite news | last = Sothern | first = Billy | title = Left to Die | pages = 19–22 | publisher = [[The Nation]] | date = 2006-01-02}}
